  "slug": "evolved-mekanism",
  "title": "Evolved Mekanism",
  "description": "Evolved Mekanism enhances Mekanism with new machine tiers and additional content",
  "body": "<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><img src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/em_banner.gif\" width=\"1004\" height=\"502\" alt=\"Banner\"></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" alt=\"separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\"></p>\n<div style=\"text-align: center; line-height: 36px;\"><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://discord.gg/nFBAXfb\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Discord&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=5865f2&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=discord&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"discord\" width=\"117\" height=\"28\"></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://github.com/iglee42\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=GitHub&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=000000&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=github&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"github\" width=\"108\" height=\"28\"></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://www.youtube.com/@iglee42\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=YouTube&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=FF0000&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=youtube&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"youtube\" width=\"118\" height=\"28\"></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/members/iglee42/projects\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=CurseForge&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=f16436&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=curseforge&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"curseforge\" width=\"143\" height=\"28\"></a><a style=\"margin-right: 0.5rem; margin-left: 0.5rem;\" href=\"https://modrinth.com/user/iglee42\" rel=\"nofollow\"><img src=\"https://img.shields.io/static/v1?label=&amp;message=Modrinth&amp;color=555555&amp;labelColor=1ace65&amp;style=for-the-badge&amp;logo=modrinth&amp;logoColor=white\" alt=\"modrinth\" width=\"129\" height=\"28\"></a></div>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" alt=\"separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 30px;\"><span style=\"color: #808080; font-size: 30px;\">Evolved Mekanism enhances Mekanism with new machine tiers and additional content<br></span></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">Current Mekanism Version Supported:<br>1.20.1: 10.4<br>1.21.1: 10.7</span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\">5 New machine tiers :</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #00da00;\"><strong>Overclocked</strong> </span>(11 slots) :</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_012f4fec-64f0-4636-b96e-761e94528c92.png\" alt=\"overclocked gui\" width=\"350\" height=\"146\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_7f022760-6736-45d5-9cdb-883000465b16.png\" alt=\"overclocked gui 2\" width=\"446\" height=\"332\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #b96ad9;\"><strong>Quantum</strong></span> (13 slots) :</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_d0da1937-02df-4bdc-8981-da53966af249.png\" alt=\"quantum gui\" width=\"390\" height=\"204\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_ec6cd516-1e1e-409f-850b-1933edfca972.png\" alt=\"quantum gui 2\" width=\"522\" height=\"332\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #f1c40f;\"><strong>Dense</strong></span> (15 slots) :</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_1686b2b2-1178-4e82-aaab-056a9facac26.png\" alt=\"dense gui\" width=\"350\" height=\"146\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_2debccdc-f85b-4910-b7d7-03421a0aaf8a.png\" alt=\"dense gui 2\" width=\"598\" height=\"332\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #202020;\"><strong>Multiversal</strong></span> (17 slots) :</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_0c13c489-817e-471a-acf2-b5f9fc285c10.png\" alt=\"multiversal gui\" width=\"350\" height=\"146\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_74b230a5-630b-4e28-b26a-4ddf3a88612b.png\" alt=\"mutliversal gui 2\" width=\"674\" height=\"332\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><span style=\"color: #fff;\"><strong>Creative</strong></span> (19 slots) :</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_aacb5ed6-127c-4bc6-89bb-c09b44764190.png\" alt=\"creative alloy\" width=\"56\" height=\"56\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">(Modpack makers, this is your time to find a craft for the Creative Alloy)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_465907dc-33b0-4522-9033-5356c0b8e0bf.png\" alt=\"creative gui\" width=\"750\" height=\"332\"></span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\" alt=\"separator\"></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Other stuff added</strong> :</span></h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Tier Installers | Alloys | Circuits | Bins | Induction | Tanks | Cells | Machine Tiers | QIO</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_569ba91d-e4f3-4c4b-9540-64c32d29c98f.png\" alt=\"More Tiered Stuff\" width=\"380\" height=\"200\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Advanced Personal Chests &amp; Barrels</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_8d01c606-6c45-4b0e-b786-ae55a736e87d.png\" alt=\"Upgraded personal storage\" width=\"344\" height=\"92\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Alloy Blocks</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_46c78c72-b991-43ff-a5fd-0955cbed9d06.png\" alt=\"alloy blocks\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Cables</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_3aa25158-1a9a-4165-b4bb-7719ec52f027.png\" alt=\"upgraded cables\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Refined Redstone</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_2be91858-7ce5-4b16-98c7-ce766d40e9aa.png\" alt=\"refined redstone recipe\"></span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\" alt=\"separator\"></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Machines added</strong> :</span></h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Antimatter Protomolecular Transmutator</strong> (<span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">APT</span>)&nbsp;<br></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_573d6a3f-379b-4d35-a057-29d6fd270df1.png\" alt=\"APT Structure\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">It<strong> </strong>is used to craft the 7th tier</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_0d952523-de7d-4ee4-90b4-ccd238c05d1a.png\" alt=\"Apt Recipe\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Here is a guide of how you can build it :</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_df9bbae4-1af8-46cf-851a-0066c6fa489b.png\" alt=\"apt guide\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">APT</span> crafting speed can be improved with the <span style=\"color: #236fa1;\">Supercharging Element</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_ec913e27-2829-4ed4-b237-4a2e3afa65b7.png\" width=\"186\" height=\"199\" alt=\"supercharging element\"></p>\n<p>You can add up to 25 in the bottom of the <span style=\"color: #843fa1;\">APT</span> (2nd layer) to go to high crafting speeds</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_270be1b8-16bf-42cd-a977-d374a03aba02.png\" width=\"263\" height=\"263\" alt=\"supercharging structure\"></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Alloyer&nbsp;</span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">combine 3 items</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_da8de736-fe5b-4e7f-b0f9-0021e380d9ff.png\" alt=\"alloyer block\" width=\"320\" height=\"331\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">It has compatibility with some mods :</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Applied Energistics 2</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_78123c99-80a9-4835-ab41-2121777d219f.png\" alt=\"ae2 recipe\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Ender IO</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_0adc7b4c-e4dd-4a72-b3a2-69af644021fb.png\" alt=\"EnderIO recipe\"><br></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Thermal &amp; Thermal Endergy</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_0719ee01-7e0b-4b63-8786-450be4c1c48a.png\" alt=\"thermal recipe\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Chemixer</strong> combine 2 items and 1 gas</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_29cfdb18-2494-4e30-81c1-bb4bcd5d7d3b.png\" alt=\"Chemixer block\" width=\"320\" height=\"331\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">It is used to craft the 8th tier</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_7735c050-1024-49ee-8cd5-faa24a6a138d.png\" alt=\"chemixer recipe\"></span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Molten Fluids System</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Thermalizer</strong> melts materials into their molten fluid version</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_171fc9eb-4225-47e4-a6e6-26cbf3fc10c2.png\" width=\"320\" height=\"332\" alt=\"thermalizer block\"></span></p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">It use Heat produced by the Resistive Heater to melt</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_2bcbba76-e9be-45d2-94a0-5ea3decd5d57.png\" alt=\"Thermalizer recipe\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Solidification Chamber</strong> solidifies molten fluid into their materials version</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_03cfa41e-a021-4db7-b905-18cbd56c9baa.png\" width=\"320\" height=\"328\" alt=\"Solidification Chamber block\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">It use Liquid Oxygen to solidify&nbsp;</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_8afdd98e-ebc8-464c-99dc-fc6cdef56b4f.png\" alt=\"Solidification recipe\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">List of Molds for Solidification Chamber (not consumed on craft)</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_fb0dcb85-3ccd-4715-9125-685e45001449.png\" alt=\"Molds\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Block Mold | Ingot Mold | Gem Mold | Nugget Mold | Dust Mold</li>\n<li>Plate Mold | Gear Mold | Rod Mold | Wire Mold | Coin Mold</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Evolved Solar Panels&nbsp;</strong>(Mekanism Generators compatibility)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_b47f9917-d095-431e-b95e-934ccb8af011.png\" width=\"700\" height=\"181\" alt=\"Upgraded solar panel\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_f728c5fb-4677-4aa9-b044-d333cee06742.png\" width=\"699\" height=\"180\" alt=\"upgraded solar panel 2\"></span></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\" alt=\"separator\"></p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Stuff &amp; Tools (Mekanism Tools compatibility)</strong> :</span></h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Better Gold Stuff &amp; Tools</span></p>\n<br>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_a6784663-e92a-40e7-99ff-727e0f149d4e.png\" width=\"118\" height=\"213\" alt=\"Better gold armor\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_bfd78854-1843-46f9-93b1-a0fd430a9c54.png\" alt=\"better gold tools\"></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Plaslitherite Stuff &amp; Tools</span></p>\n<br>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_ed3f2e0a-9e75-484e-87aa-8b3a161b999a.png\" width=\"118\" height=\"210\" alt=\"Plaslitherite armor\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_ce54b628-dc5a-410f-83e2-39d1c6b935fc.png\" alt=\"Plaslitherite tools\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\">Refined Redstone Stuff &amp; Tools</span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_39941322-91e0-46f8-ad56-884f4f1039f7.png\" width=\"118\" height=\"203\" alt=\"Refined redstone armor\"></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_8c63853f-2994-4ae1-aa9a-f5f26ab11408.png\" alt=\"Refined redstone tools\"></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\">&nbsp;</p>\n<h1><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Other additions</strong>&nbsp;:</span></h1>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Modules Units</strong></span></p>\n<p><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_0dc1560c-ed98-4c52-b4a2-9e59abd550d7.png\" alt=\"New Modules\"></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Air Affinity Unit :&nbsp;Disables the mining malus when flying. (Supported by MekaSuit Boots)</li>\n<li>Aqua Affinity Unit : Disables the mining malus when underwater. (Supported by MekaSuit Helmet)</li>\n<li>Capturing Unit : Provides a chance to loot mobs spawn eggs when killing them. (Supported by Meka-Tool)</li>\n<li>Luck Unit : Increases the chance of getting better loot. (Supported by MekaSuit Pants)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Upgrades</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_ed88c067-2fab-432f-840f-64cb18f598a5.png\" alt=\"new upgrades\"></strong></span></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Radioactive Upgrade : Allow Radioactive gas insertion. (for the Chemixer)</li>\n<li>Solar Upgrade : Increases solar production of generators. (for the Solar Generators)</li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Dimensional Mekanism Ores</strong></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/1230085/description_f2dbf470-44f6-4765-b3a4-97d9cdd972a1.png\" width=\"352\" height=\"352\" alt=\"new ores\"></strong></span></p>\n<p>Compatibility with Aether and Undergarden</p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\" alt=\"separator\"></p>\n<h1 style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 20px;\"><strong>Planned features</strong> :</span></h1>\n<ul>\n<li>Fluid Alloyer</li>\n<li>Lunar Generators</li>\n<li>Colored Machines</li>\n</ul>\n<p>and a large amount of stuff and ideas that you'll see later...</p>\n</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">&nbsp;</div>\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\">\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\" alt=\"separator\"></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://billing.sparkedhost.com/aff.php?aff=2723\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\"><img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/description/829380/description_351e5b5a-1c0d-493f-bb82-932420236878.png\" alt=\"Sparked Banner\" width=\"850\" height=\"133\"></a></p>\n<p><img style=\"display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\" src=\"https://api.iglee.fr/image/separator\" width=\"832\" height=\"14\" alt=\"separator\"></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">You can use the mod on your modpack , but you can't repost the mod on an another website !</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-size: 16px;\">Curseforge and Modrinth are the only website where the mod was posted</span></p>\n</div>",
